│                      │  [Đang chờ...]        [Chat ở đây...]                      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

## 🛠️ **TECHNICAL IMPROVEMENTS**

### **🎯 Simplified Code Structure**
- ✅ **Removed**: `CreateWaitingState()` method (800+ lines)
- ✅ **Added**: `CreateSimpleWaitingArea()` method (clean 150 lines)
- ✅ **Simplified**: Player list display logic
- ✅ **Streamlined**: UI component creation

### **📱 Modern UI Elements**

#### **🎭 Simple Character Animation**
```csharp
✅ Blue square body + circular head
✅ Golden timer icon (minimal)  
✅ Simple white eyes and smile
✅ Clean geometric design
```

#### **📋 Compact Rules Panel**
```csharp
✅ Essential information only
✅ Single line rule display
✅ Minimalist border design
✅ Clear typography hierarchy
```

#### **💬 Chat Interface (Image 1 Style)**
```csharp
✅ Tab-based design: "TRẢ LỜI" | "TRÒ CHUYỆN"
✅ Disabled waiting input: "Đang chờ..."
✅ Active chat input: "Chat ở đây..."
✅ Focus-based placeholder behavior
```

### **🔧 .NET Framework 4.7.2 Compatibility**
- ✅ **Placeholder Text**: Custom implementation using Focus events
- ✅ **Manual Input Management**: No modern UI dependencies
- ✅ **Legacy-Compatible**: Works with older framework versions
- ✅ **Error-Free Build**: All compilation issues resolved

